    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car! It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who needs a dependable daily driver without any fuss. It's been well-loved and runs great\u2014honestly, it's just a joy to be behind the wheel. I'm hoping for a quick and easy sale, so feel free to reach out with any questions or come by to see it in person. You're going to love it!",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
