      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it for its next owner. Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is super dependable and looks great too! I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019d love to see it go to a home where it\u2019ll be appreciated. Drop me a message if you want to come see it for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and a 6-speed manual gearbox. This naturally aspirated powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies to deliver instantaneous response up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damping Control (EDC) and the variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution and lateral stability. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including the replacement of rod bearings and throttle actuators\u2014essential for the longevity of this high-strung valvetrain. The suspension geometry remains true with no bushing play, providing the tactile feedback and turn-in precision expected of the M-division\u2019s finest engineering.",
      "price": 31500.0,
